rows.label: qst200701_0010
rows.name: Are both contestants ready, mo?

rows.label: qst200701_0020
rows.name: OK, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0030
rows.name: I'm good-ppo!

rows.label: qst200701_0040
rows.name:
Then let the mushroom
speed-eating contest, begin, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0050
rows.name:
Contestant Tora is off
to a flying start, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0060
rows.name:
His opponent, Idaten,
has yet to move, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0070
rows.name:
Is he captivated by the beauty of
the food? What is going on-mo?

rows.label: qst200701_0080
rows.name:
Masterpon, keep it up, mo!
Keep asking for more, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0090
rows.name: Mogumogumogumogumo!

rows.label: qst200701_0100
rows.name:
Contestant Tora is already
on his fourth plate, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0110
rows.name:
However, contestant Idaten still
shows no sign of moving, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0120
rows.name: Has he already given up the match, mo?

rows.label: qst200701_0130
rows.name:
Mo mo mo! Contestant Idaten
has finally moved, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0135
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]

rows.label: qst200701_0140
rows.name: This is amazing, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0150
rows.name:
Contestant Idaten's food is disappearing
at an unprecedented speed, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0160
rows.name:
Masterpon, pick up the pace, mo!
Here is the next plate, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0170
rows.name: Mogamogamogumogumo!

rows.label: qst200701_0180
rows.name: Time's up-mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0190
rows.name:
Wow, that was something amazing to see, mo!
I've never seen anyone eat like that, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0200
rows.name:
That was a mesmerizing
eating performance, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0210
rows.name: So cool, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0220
rows.name:
Huh? Is it over-ppo? Idaten
wants to eat more-ppo.

rows.label: qst200701_0230
rows.name:
No, no, if you do any more, my shop
will go out of business, mo...

rows.label: qst200701_0240
rows.name:
This is this time's prize, mo.
Please make do with this, mo!

rows.label: qst200701_0250
rows.name: Ooh, mushrooms-ppo!

rows.label: qst200701_0260
rows.name:
Thank you-ppo! I'll take them home
and store them right away-ppo!
